title: Jack and the Beanstalk (1952 Fantasy) Abbott & Costello: comic twist to a classic fairy tale

sources.title: Jack and the Beanstalk (1952 Fantasy) Abbott & Costello: comic twist to a classic fairy tale
sources.description:
Dim-witted Jack trades a cow for cursed magic beans, launching a sky-high beanstalk to battle a brunch-obsessed Giant. With con-man accomplice Dinklepuss, they filch golden eggs, liberate a princess from captivity, and orchestrate the ultimate gravity check for their oversize foe.

Director: Jean Yarbrough
Writers: Nathaniel Curtis, Pat Costello

Main cast:
Bud Abbott – Mr. Dinkel / Mr. Dinklepuss
Lou Costello – Jack / Jack Strong
Buddy Baer – Sgt. Riley / The Giant
Dorothy Ford – Receptionist / Polly
Barbara Brown – Mrs. Strong
Shaye Cogan – Eloise Larkin / Princess Eloise

Genres: Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical, Romance
Release date: April 12, 1952 
Filming location: California
